  "title": "[성장한의원/이수소아성장클리닉]성조숙증 증상, 치료방법",
  "addDate": "2013. 8. 17.",
  "categoryNo": "10",
  "parentCategoryNo": "9",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110174315463",
  "html_size": 188132,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110174315463\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110174315463\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div class=\"view\" style='font-family: \"3028548_9\"; font-size: 9pt;'><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">[성장한의원/이수소아성장클리닉]성조숙증 증상, 치료방법</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">의학의 발달과 의식주 해결로 과거 문제가 됐던 여러 질환들은 발생 비율이 크게 줄었습니다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;하지만 환경오염과 식생활의 변화등 원인으로 서서히 환자가 늘어나는 질활들도 있는데 이 중 하나가 성조숙증 입니다 </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/72e60ff15d7fc326.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"236\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 655px; rheight: 282px;\" id=\"20130817_180/isuhani_1376709617495SUFJ6_PNG/%C1%B6%BC%F7%C1%F51.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E6A3C7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/72e60ff15d7fc326.png\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">성조숙증은 남자는 9세 여자는 8세 이전의 아이들의 또래보다 빠른 성숙을 보이는 것을 말합니다 </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">보통의 경우는 내 나이에 맞게 2차성징 과정을 거치면서 성장을 지속적으로 해나가게 되는데</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;성조숙증 아이들은 일찍 이 과정이 시작됩니다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 108, 0);\">성조숙증 증상</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 여자아이는 가슴에 멍울이 잡히고 초경을 시작하고 </p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 남자아이는 음모가 자라고 변성기가 찾아옵니다</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 땀 냄새와 머리 냄새가 진하게 풍깁니다</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 성격이 급해지고 감정의 기복이 심해집니다</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 얼굴에 피지와 여드름이 생깁니다</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 체중이 급증하고 지방량 증가합니다</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 성에 대한 호기심이 증가합니다</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e165c09e59892657.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 673px; rheight: 441px;\" id=\"20130817_71/isuhani_1376709935503BdPPw_PNG/%C1%B6%BC%F7%C1%F52.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E6A3C7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e165c09e59892657.png\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">만약 본인의 자녀에게 이러한 증상이 일찍 나타난다면 성조숙증을 생각해봐야 합니다 </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">일부 부모는 일찍 키가 자라나는 것을 또래와 비교하며 오히려 좋아 하지만&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">왜 성조숙증이 문제가 되는지 이유를 알아야 합니다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">성조숙증 환자는 빠른 성장이 일어나는 만큼 또래보다 일찍 성장이 끝나는 경우가 많습니다. </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그 결과 성인이 되어서는 평균키에 못미치게 됩니다 </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/15e8167c3507a849.png\" width=\"288\" height=\"256\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 288px; rheight: 256px;\" id=\"20130817_86/isuhani_13767102194070vQAT_PNG/%C1%B6%BC%F7%C1%F53.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E6A3C7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/15e8167c3507a849.png\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">성조숙증은 왜 생기는 것일까요? 다양한 원인들이 이야기 되지만 대표적인 것이 환경호르몬과 식생활 문제입니다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;공장의 매연과 같이 산업활동의 과정에서 생겨나는 물질인 환경 호르몬은&nbsp; 인체 내에 들어가게 되면</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;여러 기관들에 환란을 가져오며 비정상적인 기능을 하게끔 만듭니다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">하지만 성조숙증을 치료하기란 쉽지 않습니다 문제되는 요인을 정확히 파악하기가 어려우며 이미 발생한 성장과정을 되돌릴 수도 없기 때문입니다 따라서 성조숙증 치료는 성장이 가능한 동안 문제없이 최대한의 성장이 이뤄질 수 있도록 도와주는 것이 중요합니다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/503028daf449b15e.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"364\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 554px; rheight: 367px;\" id=\"20130817_263/isuhani_1376710554288QlM1h_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%E52.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E6A3C7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/503028daf449b15e.png\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 0, 124);\">이수 성장한의원에서 성조숙증 치료는 문제의 요인을 찾아 치료를 통해 해결하고</span></strong>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 0, 124);\">&nbsp;정상적인 성장이 이뤄지도록 도움을 줍니다</span></strong>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 0, 124);\">&#65279;</span></strong>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 162);\">&lt;&lt;이수 소아성장클리닉&#65279;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 162);\">&nbsp;진료시간안내&gt;&gt;</span></strong>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 162);\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/08fbda3c5befd120.png\" width=\"545\" height=\"171\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 545px; rheight: 171px;\" id=\"20130817_155/isuhani_1376710722726t5sUU_PNG/%C1%F8%B7%E1%BD%C3%B0%A3.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E6A3C7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/08fbda3c5befd120.png\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n </div>\r\n </div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
